{"tid":1720174,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一個11月15日罷post都無??","createTime":"2019-11-14T09:19:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T14:35:39.000Z","uid":145730,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3f24d22534133591d479896a04a2892697f5f4fb","tid":1720174,"uid":145730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T09:19:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>點解可以一個聽日三罷嘅post都無??</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n《左傳．莊公十年》：「夫戰，勇氣也。一鼓作氣，再而衰，三而竭。彼竭我盈。」<br />\n<br />\n春秋時，齊國攻打魯國，魯莊公準備親自領兵迎戰。這時，有個叫曹劌的人主動要求跟莊公一起迎戰。當齊魯兩軍在戰場上擺好陣勢後，齊軍擊鼓進攻，魯莊公也想下令擂鼓迎戰，但兩次都被曹劌攔住。直到齊軍第三次擊鼓時，曹劌才讓魯莊公下令擂鼓進軍，結果把齊軍打得大敗。 打了勝仗後，魯莊公問曹劌獲勝的原因。曹劌說：「打仗憑的是一股勇氣。齊軍第一次擊鼓時勇氣最足，第二次擊鼓時勇氣便有所衰退，第三次擊鼓時勇氣已完全衰竭了，而我軍卻是第一次擊鼓，勇氣最足，所以一鼓作氣，打敗了齊軍。」"},{"pid":"071f0914d491d8a20e0cf9aecff7d3a52ec7e7e0","tid":1720174,"uid":41260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T09:20:11.000Z","msg":"山田巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a9f4e4f8e1c47a625e4eb13ec383e8a8944eb7e","tid":1720174,"uid":63298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T09:20:35.000Z","msg":"繼續罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b3fc0674365d84e71dfa03cf854d7e76c6158c6","tid":1720174,"uid":78666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T09:21:20.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"5f6054f0cb115456a1ca32ae647d4774a2731238","tid":1720174,"uid":14333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T09:21:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1719744\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1719744</a>"},{"pid":"5828e67023855d38ef6367192d7cc31a5e451c2e","tid":1720174,"uid":36420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T09:21:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pi